author: Kuokka77
description:
Some Xyce's YM work.

Tracklist:

00:00 Bassez
03:13 O.K.
06:40 Wiggle

Art in order of appearance:

Asthor - "Cyber Wolf" (7th at BCC Party 2025 C64 gfx compo)
The Sarge - "Brain Damage" (1st at Mysdata 2025 C64 gfx compo)
d4ng3r - "Cybergirl" (4th at Kozmos 2025 mixed compo)

French CA4003290 Atari STe with new Mean Well RPD-60A PSU (SidecarTridge.com variety). Playback using SND Player v1.51. Brainworx VST effects applied.

STe hardware has its issues and mine is not an exception. The infamous DAC whistle was removed using iZotope RX spectral de-noiser. DMA audio crackling, while not 100% eliminated, got improved dramatically after applying Exxos STE DAC CRACKLES POP FIX (additional grounding for U500 and U501 via bodge wires). STe also has very hot RCA outputs. Luckily RME Babyface Pro FS in professional +4 dBu recording reference level mode can take it without clipping.
title: Atari music: Xyce times three (STe🎧bx_)
